snippet.title: Spyragon: Crazy Moves Medley
snippet.description:
Spyragon is available to play on the iOS App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/spyragon/id1584715775

With Spyragon Classic,  it's possible to create an insane combination of matches.  See some of the craziest boards we have seen, including 3 Full Hexagons exploding at once, 14-15 pointed Stars, 5 Combos on a single board, and more!

00:00 - 15-Pointed Yellow Star + 3 Full-Hexagons
00:22 - 14-Pointed Orange Star + 2 Full-Hexagons
00:44 - 5 Combos (1 3-Color Combo + 4 2-Color Combos)
01:09 - 14-Pointed Red Star + Combo + 2 Full Hexagons
01:23 - 11-Pointed Purple Star + 2 Combos + Full Hexagon
01:54 - 9-Pointed Green Star + 3 Combos + Full Hexagon
02:14 - 5 Combos (2 3-Color Combos + 3 2-Color Combos)
02:35 - 4 Combos + Unlocking of Level 9

Directions available at: https://spyraverse.com

Also follow us on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter: @spyraverse
